Bruno Bolet was the proud owner of the "Whisperer," a crystal skull rumored to protect its holder from almost any cause of death except murder. When Bruno passed away, his nephew Henry came to wrap up his affairs, but he couldn find the skull among the clutter of the creepy Bolet manor. Youll need to team up with Nancys best friend Bess Marvin to find this mystical artifact before it falls into the wrong hands!
Designed for players 10 and older, the search is on for an unearthly artifact in New Orleans in this fun mystery game, Nancy Drew: The Legend of the Crystal Skull.
